            <path d="M9 19C9 20.105 7.657 21 6 21C4.343 21 3 20.105 3 19C3 17.895 4.343 17 6 17C7.657 17 9 17.895 9 19ZM9 19V5L21 3V17M21 17C21 18.105 19.657 19 18 19C16.343 19 15 18.105 15 17C15 15.895 16.343 15 18 15C19.657 15 21 15.895 21 17ZM9 9L21 7" />
